components.templateData:
<ng-container>
  <app-typography [bold]="600" [size]="1.2">
    {{ label }}
  </app-typography>
  <button mat-icon-button color="primary" [matMenuTriggerFor]="menu">
    <mat-icon> arrow_drop_down </mat-icon>
  </button>
  <mat-menu #menu="matMenu" xPosition="before">
    <button
      mat-menu-item
      *ngFor="let option of options"
      (click)="onCOptionSelect(option.value)"
    >
      <app-typography> {{ option.label }}</app-typography>
    </button>
  </mat-menu>
</ng-container>

components.name: ColumnFormComponent
DashboardComponent
components.templateData:
<mat-sidenav-container class="sidenav-container">
  <mat-sidenav
    #drawer
    class="sidenav"
    fixedInViewport
    [attr.role]="(isHandset$ | async) ? 'dialog' : 'navigation'"
    [mode]="(isHandset$ | async) ? 'over' : 'side'"
    opened="false"
  >
  </mat-sidenav>
  <mat-sidenav-content>
    <ng-content select="[navbar]"></ng-content>
  </mat-sidenav-content>
</mat-sidenav-container>

styleUrlsData.data: @import "../../../../styles/styles";

components.templateData:
<mat-form-field  [appearance]="disabled ? 'fill' : 'outline'">
  <mat-label>{{ label }}</mat-label>

  <input
    type="text"
    matInput
    [formControl]="control"
    [matAutocomplete]="auto"
  />
  <mat-autocomplete
    autoActiveFirstOption
    #auto="matAutocomplete"
    (optionSelected)="onOptionSelected($event)"
  >
    <mat-option *ngFor="let option of options" [value]="option.value">
      {{ option.key }}
    </mat-option>
  </mat-autocomplete>
</mat-form-field>
